*yaala-0.7.3-r1 (03 Apr 2013)

  03 Apr 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org>
  +files/yaala-0.7.3-r1-correct-paths.patch, +yaala-0.7.3-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Taking maintainership. Bump: Added required perl dependencies and two optional
  dependencies gd and storable as per the scripts and site which users, this
  will bring more functionality to the user. Revised the install function to
  install to the proper locations (eg. /etc), also added patches in src_prepare
  such that the proper config and var directories are used by Yaala by default.
  Also made the ebuild slightly more maintainable. Extensively tested.

  13 Mar 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> yaala-0.6.3.ebuild,
  yaala-0.7.2.ebuild, yaala-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Resolved repoman warnings.

